The paper deals with text classification, which is a natural language processing (NLP) task, and proposes a new method for Capsule Networks (CapsNets) in this domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The proposed routing algorithm is based on k-means clustering theory, which falls under the category of unsupervised learning (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on several text classification datasets, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
